"http://www.xynthetic.com/\">Xynthetic</a></li>\r\n	<li> <a href=\"http://zymogen.net\">Zymogen</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSome other online labels I\'ve come across that have been interesting in one way or another...\r\n\r\n<script src=\"http://del.icio.us/feeds/js/craque/labels?tags;count=100;title=labels;bullet=%C2%BB;icon;sort=alpha\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>','Music Labels',0,'','inherit','open','open','','4-revision','','','2008-07-11 10:18:51','2008-07-11 17:18:51','',4,'http://sounding.com/blog/?p=109',0,'revision','',0),(110,2,'2008-07-29 16:34:56','2008-07-29 23:34:56','Here\'s a live set from the guys at <a href=\"http://erotus.net\" target=\"_blank\">Erotus</a> (Blamstrain\'s new label) celebrating its launch, featured in the <a href=\"www.uudenmusiikinfestivaali.org\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Viides Uuden Musiikin Festivaali</em></a>, or \"Fifth Festival for New Music\", held in Kupittaanpuisto, Turku, Finland.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"Erotus_Records_-_Label_Launch_at_Festival_For_New_Music_5_-_25-07-2008.mp3\" target=\"_blank\">Download it</a> to hear <strong>area</strong>, <strong>asketix</strong>, <strong>blamstrain</strong>, <strong>ercola</strong>, and <strong>mk10</strong> (not necessarily in that order) throw down a continuous two and a half hour set of glitch-filled, sometimes psychedelic, always atmospheric minimal techno from 25 July in Finland.','Erotus Records Kickoff Set',0,'','publish','open','open','','erotus-records-kickoff-set','','','2008-07-29 17:22:55','2008-07-30 00:22:55','',0,'http://sounding.com/blog/?p=110',0,'post','',0),(111,2,'2008-07-29 16:34:00','2008-07-29 23:34:00','Here\'s a live set from the guys at <a href=\"http://erotus.net\" target=\"_blank\">Erotus</a> (Blamstrain\'s new label), featured in the <a href=\"www.uudenmusiikinfestivaali.org\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Viides Uuden Musiikin Festivaali</em></a>, or \"Fifth Festival for New Music\", held in Kupittaanpuisto, Turku, Finland.\n\n<a href=\"Erotus_Records_-_Label_Launch_a