is pieced out and chopped as if... Burroughsian perversions, perhaps? Joycean slips of the tongue, a composting of ideas and pursuasions that melt together as if merging stained...\r\n\r\n\"Sextant\" is a poem I wrote around 2004:\r\n<blockquote>Blue chrome carriage\r\nMouse brown hair\r\nDark shadowed eyes\r\nCold mean stare\r\n\r\nWhite-armed glove driver\r\nSunshine in your car\r\nIf the signal never signaled\r\nWould you have gone that far?</blockquote>\r\nThe <a href=\"http://www.audiobulb.com/albums/AB019/AB019.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Audiobulb release page</a> contains links to eMusic, iTunes, Thrill Jockey and boomkat sites for purchasing the album. There\'s also an interview with me with some other details about the album and music and things like that, with clips from some of the tracks I\'ve mentioned here.\r\n\r\nAs if you haven\'t had enough of me already, <a href=\"http://earslend.blogspot.com/2009/04/crunchy-seam.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lend Me Your Ears has a feature on Supple</a> and some of my other netlabel releases, as well as an other interview with very different questions from the Audiobulb one, so it\'s not repeating the same info, I promise! He also has a free version of \"Navfrakure\" available for download.','\"Supple\" out now on Audiobulb',0,'','inherit','open','open','','280-revision-9','','','2009-04-07 18:08:17','2009-04-08 02:08:17','',280,'http://sounding.com/blog/?p=289',0,'revision','',0),(290,2,'2009-04-07 18:08:22','2009-04-08 02:08:22','[caption id=\"attachment_279\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"300\" caption=\"artwork by gl0tch, mastered by twerk\"]<a href=\"http://audiobulb.com\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-279\" title=\"Craque: Supple\" src=\"https://sounding.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/supple-cover-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"artwork by gl0tch, mastering by twerk\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nPresenting: an album of electro-acoustic music through a personal expression of non-intention.\r\n\r\