n','open','','now-playing-2','','','2012-03-15 10:36:23','2012-03-15 17:36:23','',0,'http://sounding.com/blog/?p=766',0,'post','',0),(763,2,'2012-03-02 12:12:59','2012-03-02 20:12:59','','20120302-121049.jpg',0,'','inherit','open','open','','20120302-121049-jpg','','','2012-03-02 12:12:59','2012-03-02 20:12:59','',764,'http://sounding.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/20120302-121049.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(764,2,'2012-03-02 12:13:00','2012-03-02 20:13:00','<a href=\"https://sounding.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/20120302-121049.jpg\"><img src=\"https://sounding.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/20120302-121049.jpg\" alt=\"20120302-121049.jpg\" class=\"alignnone size-full\" /></a>\n\nWe own this D battery operated \"mini organ\" that has a real blower inside and some kind of reed system... I haven\'t taken it apart yet to see, and somewhat afraid of breaking it, but it works and sounds really cool!','Proll Toys Mini Organ',0,'','publish','open','open','','proll-toys-mini-organ','','','2012-03-02 12:13:00','2012-03-02 20:13:00','',0,'http://sounding.com/blog/?p=764',0,'post','',0),(765,2,'2012-03-02 12:13:00','2012-03-02 20:13:00','','Auto Draft',0,'','inherit','open','open','','764-revision','','','2012-03-02 12:13:00','2012-03-02 20:13:00','',764,'http://sounding.com/blog/2012/03/02/764-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(767,2,'2012-03-14 15:19:58','2012-03-14 22:19:58','','Auto Draft',0,'','inherit','open','open','','766-revision','','','2012-03-14 15:19:58','2012-03-14 22:19:58','',766,'http://sounding.com/blog/2012/03/14/766-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(749,2,'2012-02-17 07:56:58','2012-02-17 15:56:58','Lackluster ::: <em>The Invisible Spanish Inquisition</em>\n\nSteve Martin & The Steep Canyon Rangers ::: <em>Rare Bird Alert</em>\n\nMarcus Fischer ::: <em>Collected Dust</em>\n\nWoob ::: <em>Paradigm Flux</em>\n\nSkirt ::: <em>Horizontal Ground</em>','Now Playing',0,'','inherit','open','open','','746-revision-3','','','2012-02-17 07:56:58','